data.description: Beautiful Brick 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in BarX Subdivision on 2.04 acres surrounded by wildlife. There is a large acreage tract backing up to the property allowing great privacy . This home is a family's dream home with a 18,000 gallon swimming pool and covered pergolas ready for outdoor fun! This home features raised inset ceilings in all rooms, Jack and Jill bathroom between bedrooms, office/study, or possible 4th bedroom, stainless appliances, breakfast nook, formal dining room, two living areas(living room/family room) and a wood burning fireplace.Home has a motion sensing camera security system and recording monitor system valued at $16,000. Easy access to Highway 35. The home has never flooded!
